20 gauge gold plated head pin. I have a 6mm

00:00:42.390 --> 00:00:45.850
28 gauge jump ring and you do need a

00:00:45.850 --> 00:00:50.089
a larger size ring to fit through the top of your pendant

00:00:50.089 --> 00:00:53.350
and then I just have a gold plated bali style earring hook

00:00:53.350 --> 00:00:56.900
So I'm just gonna show you how to do one
earring

